  <portpage logo="../amigappc/amigappc.gif" logoheight="95"
    logowidth="79">
    <portabout>
      <para>NetBSD/amigappc is a very experimental port to the
        PowerPC-based Amiga expansion boards as manufactured by Phase
        5.</para>

      <para>Supported peripheral devices will basically be the same as
        with <ulink url="../amiga/">NetBSD/amiga</ulink>. We do not plan
        to create a NetBSD-4.0 binary release, but development will
        continue and is in fact, easier, now that cross-compilation of
        the base system is supported within NetBSD-current.</para>

      <para>A recipe to create a NetBSD/AmigaPPC kernel and a minimal
        system to test it will appear here shortly.</para>
    </portabout>

